# Example Data for KINMET

This folder contains example data provided solely for
demonstration and testing of the KINMET software.

## example1_head_impact.csv
## example2_head_impact.csv

- Synthetic 6-DOF head kinematic data for 120 milliseconds (10 pre-impact and 110 post-impact)
- Units:
  - Time: microseconds
  - Linear acceleration: g
  - Angular velocity: deg/s

This file can be used to:
- Preview the GUI functionality
- Test column mapping and unit conversion
- Generate a sample PDF report


